<plot>Daisy Smith, a floater and non-desirable citizen in most societies, seeks refuge on a tropical island in the South Seas. She meets Jim Curtis, another society-outcast and a piece of human driftwood, and a romance takes place that regenerates both and they sail back to the United States determined to start life anew.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?160119</url></doc>
